dct_alternative_sm: Times Map of the western campaign
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows woods, cities and towns, roads, railways, canals, waterways, forts, boundaries.
Probably taken from The Times War Atlas.
